channel.title: Java Heap Space
channel.description:
Hello, so I have all the mapdata for a 530 put in to the XenoRune 530 cleaned that was released by [b]southpark[/b]. Anyway, I get into the game, I want to teleport to the tutorial dungeon by ::tele, but it always come up with the Java Heap Space error. Every other place works besides the coords 2522 5000. Do I need to change something within my reading mapdata file or something wrong with the whole area in general.
It's a lot to read just for a help but it has all information of the source and everything I've changed before the error.
Thanks in advance
